    <hr></hr>
    <h2 {...{
      "id": "maniac-mansion-1987"
    }}>{`Maniac Mansion (1987) `}<a id="maniac"></a></h2>
    <p>{`Maniac Mansion was the first game to use the SCUMM scripting language.`}</p>
    <p>{`The game follows Dave Miller and a group of his friends as they break into a strange mansion in an attempt to rescue Dave's girlfriend Sandy and stop the evil purple meteor from taking over the world. The game has a group of six characters to choose from (Dave must always be in your party), and multiple possible endings.`}</p>
    <table>
      <thead parentName="table">
